Class ValueContext<A,L,W>

  • Object
    • ValueContext<A,L,W>
  • Type Parameters:
    A - The type of the node's ID value
    L - The type of the node's label metadata
    W - The type of the weight metadata on the edges
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Context<A,ValueNode<A,L>,ValueEdge<A,L,W>,HashSet<ValueEdge<A,L,W>>>

    public final class ValueContext<A,L,W>
extends Object
implements Context<A,ValueNode<A,L>,ValueEdge<A,L,W>,HashSet<ValueEdge<A,L,W>>>
    A Context which is a value object, isomorphic to a tuple containing its node, a set of edges into the node, and a set of edges coming out of the node
